WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.089
This is AkamaiForms. Your team signs in with an account your office controls —

00:06.139 --> 00:12.228
grant it, revoke it, your call. One sign-in... and the day is waiting for you.

00:15.000 --> 00:20.485
This is the preflight review console — and the morning is already sorted.

00:20.535 --> 00:23.290
Seven packets came through overnight.

00:23.340 --> 00:28.370
Every one has been read, checked, and filed before anyone sat down.

00:28.420 --> 00:33.450
The queue reads top to bottom, in the order your attention matters:

00:33.500 --> 00:39.061
one needs a person... four need fixes... and two are cleared, and waiting.

00:40.311 --> 00:43.656
Start where you're needed most. On this packet,

00:43.706 --> 00:49.291
the name on the application and the name on the identity documents are close —

00:49.341 --> 00:54.060
but they are not the same. On identity, the system does not guess.

00:54.110 --> 00:59.983
It shows you exactly what it read, on which document — and it waits for your call.

01:01.233 --> 01:05.961
Next, a fix. Every attachment recognized for what it is.

01:06.011 --> 01:11.591
Every finding written in plain language — which form, which field,

01:11.641 --> 01:13.383
what's wrong with it.

01:14.633 --> 01:19.399
And the reply is already written — addressed to the applicant,

01:19.449 --> 01:23.127
naming every missing item. Nothing sends itself.

01:23.177 --> 01:27.244
A person reads this letter, and a person clicks send.

01:27.294 --> 01:32.215
The applicant fixes everything in one round... instead of three.

01:33.465 --> 01:38.103
And the good news story: two packets came in complete.

01:38.153 --> 01:44.961
Both forms, the IDs, every rule satisfied. Cleared — your reviewer starts here.

01:46.211 --> 01:48.972
One more thing, for the auditors.

01:49.022 --> 01:54.081
Every step the system took is written into a sealed logbook.

01:54.131 --> 01:58.254
Watch — we re-check it on the spot. Chain intact.

01:58.304 --> 02:01.234
Provable today, provable next year.

02:02.484 --> 02:08.329
That's the whole experience. Sign in — and the clerical work is already done.

02:08.379 --> 02:13.305
Nothing ever goes out without a person approving it. AkamaiForms.

02:13.355 --> 02:15.678
Every submission, review ready.
